code-item.returns:
make_field_translator(std::move(s), std::forward<Appendices>(appendices)...) (first overload) or make_field_translator(std::allocator_arg, alloc, std::move(s), std::forward<Appendices>(appendices)...) (second overload) where s is an object constructed as follows:
if values.push_back(t) is a valid expression where t is an rvalue of typename Container::value_type, std::back_inserter(values),
otherwise, std::inserter(values, values.end()).
